保组织成员。杰西在新书里娓娓道来的，正是九年前的</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/97564/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/85226/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-06-30/201906301561896361.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/85226/">黄昏的清兵卫</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%AE%AB%E6%B3%BD%E7%90%86%E6%83%A0------------/" target="_blank">宫泽理惠</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%9C%9F%E7%94%B0%E5%B9%BF%E4%B9%8B------------/" target="_blank">真田广之</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%A4%A7%E6%9D%89%E6%B6%9F------------/" target="_blank">大杉涟</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B0%E6%B4%8B%E6%AC%A1--------/" target="_blank">山田洋次</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/8/" target="_blank">爱情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-----------/" target="_blank">日本</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2002/" target="_blank">2002</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>幕府末年的海阪藩，下级武士清兵卫（真田广之）在妻子病逝后，以微薄薪俸独自照料痴呆老母和两个年幼女儿，由于每日结束工作后都是匆匆回家从不参加应酬，他被同僚们戏称为“黄昏的清兵卫”&nbsp;　　与清兵卫青梅竹马的朋江（宫泽里惠）同丈夫离婚回到娘家后，常到清兵卫家代他照顾母亲和女儿，招来不少蜚言蜚语。清</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/85226/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/49207/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2018-03-31/201803311522482775.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1280高清国语中字版</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/49207/">海昏侯传奇之藏锋</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%8D%A2%E6%98%93------------/" target="_blank">卢易</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E5%AD%90%E4%BF%8A------------/" target="_blank">张子俊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E8%AF%97%E4%BD%B3------------/" target="_blank">黄诗佳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%A2%85%E6%B4%8B------------/" target="_blank">梅洋</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%8B%8F%E5%89%91%E9%A2%96--------/" target="_blank">苏剑颖</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>山阳郡城，一桩刺杀失踪案，将西汉被废帝王刘贺卷入一场积怨多年的皇权斗争冷艳的绣衣使者，心狠手辣的朝廷大司马，冷血的长安御史悉数登场。宿命驱使下，刘贺、黛紧紧纠葛，他们的前世今生也被慢慢揭开。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/49207/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/76437/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-03-11/201903111552249263.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/76437/">黄昏恋</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%8E%AB%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E5%88%87%E7%93%A6%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%9A------------/" target="_blank">莫里斯·切瓦力亚</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%A5%A5%E9%BB%9B%E4%B8%BD%C2%B7%E8%B5%AB%E6%9C%AC------------/" target="_blank">奥黛丽·赫本</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%8A%A0%E9%87%8C%C2%B7%E5%BA%93------------/" target="_blank">加里·库</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%AF%94%E5%88%A9%C2%B7%E6%8